column5: I think you misunderstood him. He meant clicking the link from the autobot, not clicking the ads on the site.

I am so sorry, I can't even imagine the amount of pain you're suffering from right now, from your description it seems like she was truly an angel. I hope that the monsters that did it will be punished. Stay strong, I feel like that's what she would've wanted you to do. Please accept my condolences.
Batman: Curse of the White Knight
